me.com/news/music/beyonces-foundation-announces-2-5million-donation-to-la-wildfire-relief-3828303">碧昂斯的Beygood基金会已捐赠了250万美元，</a>以帮助为洛杉矶野火提供救济。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paris-hilton-launches-fund-for-families-displaced-by-the-la-wildfires-3828081">巴黎·希尔顿（Paris Hilton）还为被大火流离失所的家庭开设了一项基金</a>，承诺要捐款100,000美元，最高可达100,000美元的捐款。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dave-grohl-spent-birthday-making-meals-for-families-hit-by-la-wildfires-3829226">戴夫·格罗尔（Dave Grohl）还为受到影响的家庭度过了生日</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3827798" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827798" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827798" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/LA-Wildfires.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/LA-Wildfires.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/LA-Wildfires-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/LA-Wildfires-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/LA-Wildfires-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/LA-Wildfires-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/LA-Wildfires-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827798" class="wp-caption-text">洛杉矶日落大道的野火（信用：Apu Gomes/Getty Images）</figcaption></figure><p>美国 - 墨西哥乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/american-mexican-fuerza-regida-rent-entire-hotel-shelter-victims-wildfires-3828174">Fuerza Regida已将整个酒店出租了一个星期，以庇护50个逃离野火的家庭</a>。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-urges-brands-gifting-her-clothing-to-instead-donate-it-to-those-affected-by-horrific-la-wildfires-3828185">Charli XCX呼吁品牌向她的衣服赠送，以“将其[将其送给真正需要它的人。”</a>然后，她分享了由设计师拉娜·杰伊·拉基（Lana Jay Lackey）组织的服装驱动器的细节，敦促其他人加入她的捐款。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ariana-grande">阿丽亚娜·格兰德（Ariana Grande）</a> ，比利·埃里什（Billie Eilish）等人<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/entertainment-world-reacts-to-heart-wrenching-los-angeles-wildfires-3827340">对野火造成的“令人心碎”的破坏做出了反应</a>，为需要帮助的人分享了资源联系。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/la-music-community-tragic-wildfires-long-lasting-effects-3828259">洛杉矶音乐界的成员还与<i>NME</i>谈到了遭受重创</a>，许多场所，工作室和艺术家都受到大火的影响。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/hayley-williams-st-vincent-finneas-and-more-announced-for-gve-a-fck-la-wildfires-benefit-concert-3832427">海莉·威廉姆斯（Hayley Williams），圣文森特（St. Vincent），芬内亚斯（Finneas）等宣布的“ g*ve af*ck&#39;la wildfires福利音乐会”</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
